{"value":"[{\"id\":424,\"question\":\"What is the primary purpose of including personal anecdotes in a sports biography?\",\"option_a\":\"To increase the book's length without adding value\",\"option_b\":\"To illustrate the athlete's character and journey\",\"option_c\":\"To distract from factual errors\",\"option_d\":\"To focus solely on the athlete's achievements\",\"correct_option\":\"To illustrate the athlete's character and journey\"},{\"id\":425,\"question\":\"Which element is essential for establishing credibility when writing a sports biography?\",\"option_a\":\"Using only first-person interviews\",\"option_b\":\"Citing verifiable sources and facts\",\"option_c\":\"Including fictionalized scenes\",\"option_d\":\"Avoiding any mention of team dynamics\",\"correct_option\":\"Citing verifiable sources and facts\"},{\"id\":426,\"question\":\"When describing an athlete's early life, a biographer should prioritize:\",\"option_a\":\"Highlighting only championship moments\",\"option_b\":\"Detailing formative experiences that shaped their career\",\"option_c\":\"Omitting family background\",\"option_d\":\"Focusing exclusively on college statistics\",\"correct_option\":\"Detailing formative experiences that shaped their career\"},{\"id\":427,\"question\":\"What is the recommended approach for handling controversial moments in an athlete's career?\",\"option_a\":\"Ignoring them entirely to keep the narrative positive\",\"option_b\":\"Presenting a balanced view that includes facts, context, and multiple perspectives\",\"option_c\":\"Exaggerating the impact to attract readers\",\"option_d\":\"Using them as the main focus of the biography\",\"correct_option\":\"Presenting a balanced view that includes facts, context, and multiple perspectives\"}]","expires":1768158036,"created":1768071636}